application.controllers

Class FilmController

  • java.lang.Object
    • application.controllers.MainController
      • application.controllers.FilmController

  • public class FilmController
extends MainController
    Purpose:
    Display Film and Screening information, and
    and manipulate Film and Screening objects
    Description:
    Contains all methods manipulating films and screenings,
    and sets up the views primarily governed with film and
    screening tables and manipulation (FilmEmployee and
    FilmCustomer (displaying information about a given film),
    NewFilm (for adding new films), NewScreening (for adding new
    screenings), NewBooking (for displaying a screenings table and
    choosing one for a new booking), and ScreeningsCustomer and
    ScreeningsEmployee (for displaying a list of screenings for
    a given film)).
    Version:
    $Date: 2017/12/14 16:00:00 $
    Author:
    Zaid Al Lahham and Aleksi Anttila
